DEBUG:neo4j.io:[#6EB1]  C: RUN 'CALL db.index.fulltext.queryNodes("episode_content", $query, {limit: $limit})\n            YIELD node AS episode, score\n            MATCH (e:Episodic)\n            WHERE e.uuid = episode.uuid\n            \nAND e.group_id IN $group_ids\n            RETURN\n            \n    e.uuid AS uuid,\n    e.name AS name,\n    e.group_id AS group_id,\n    e.created_at AS created_at,\n    e.source AS source,\n    e.source_description AS source_description,\n    e.content AS content,\n    e.valid_at AS valid_at,\n    e.entity_edges AS entity_edges\n\n            ORDER BY score DESC\n            LIMIT $limit\n            ' {'database_': 'neo4j', 'query': 'group_id:"personal-agent-default" AND (在支付系统重构项目里，\\Alice 提出把订单服务和库存服务解耦。她认为服务降级可以保护核心下单链路，但推荐模块会干扰支付流程。第一阶段方案包括 \\Redis 限流、熔断器和异步消息队列。)', 'limit': 20, 'group_ids': ['personal-agent-default']} {}
